   <h1>RE: [VB] trip report--kinda long</h1>
   <b>&quot;mpaubh&quot; &lt;mpaubh_at_netzero_dot_net&gt;</b><br/>
   <i>2002-05-03 00:08:44+00</i><br/>
   <br/>
   <pre>Excellent trip report, the long trips are usually the best because of the
unknown. I remember my trip in 96 in a 79 westy from Los Angeles all the way
to Georgia by myself, although I was alone it still was the best trip
because of all the people I met along the way .
Brian Hudson

-----Original Message-----
From: matthew j. ramsey [mailto:mattthewriter_at_hotmail_dot_com]
Sent: Thursday, May 02, 2002 2:29 PM
To: alisalowman_at_hotmail_dot_com; amy_at_csmonitor_dot_com;
bkroening_at_mail.holton.k12.ks_dot_us; bookworm_1977_at_yahoo_dot_com;
